reviewText: Not a particularly well made film.

"Strategic Leadership Toward Sustainability"  is a very motivating DVD.  Featuring Dr. Daryl Green and Brandi Reilly, It goes into the concepts of leadership and sustainability, addressing issues of strategic leadership in today's global organizations.  It recognizes the role of sustainability and describes the current business environment and topics of current interest in business.  Great price, well worth the money.  Highly recommended!

Ok. let me give me my personal opinion on this DVD. I was highly motivated by this product and recommend this to my friends in my school.
Thanks amazon.
